node.title: Zola: Film based on a viral Twitter thread sees strippers' road trip descend into chaos
node.alt: White woman and black woman wearing makeup and minimal clothing sit in dressing room and take selfie in mirror.
node.description: This stranger-than-fiction odyssey reveals the seedy and dangerous underworld of sex trafficking when a Hooters waitress is conned by a customer and her dodgy pimp.
node.content: ["\"You wanna hear a story about why me and this bitch here fell out? It's kind of long but full of suspense.\""]
